data.description: Converted garage could be 4th bedroom! This beautiful home is located in the Northeast side of San Antonio- minutes away from Converse, Universal City, Live Oak, and Randalph AFB.    This is a 4 bedroom home with 2 full baths, a spacious living room with a cozy fire place, separate dining room, breakfast bar, and lovely patio to enjoy a warm cup of coffee as the weather cools down! The backyard is large and includes a shed that can be used for storage or a small office.     Settle down for the holidays in this beautiful home!
